{"tid":1855790,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"去左黃大仙拜神寫光復香港比人打","createTime":"2020-02-01T09:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T06:26:01.000Z","uid":6783,"like":244,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9f4ed4261cde46349fdca5beacfd39664b50a8","tid":1855790,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"今日同女朋友去黃大仙廟到拜神 <br />\n上完香有得寫下願望<br />\n我係個到寫光復香港<br />\n隔離有個黑黑實實既無啦啦一拳打落我隻手到<br />\n仲問我係咪曱甴 我除口罩對住佢噴口水<br />\n係佢反應唔切個陣我再吐多幾啖就跑走<br />\n死黑警我知你一定有mon post<br />\n唔好以為大隻就唔會肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d09bd7ef1fa0c27f8791343222b52c621e3e0f","tid":1855790,"uid":254504,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"正 追鳩住佢噴"},{"pid":"3867ad09ab07545b9eb64fbe1c37753fd1905713","tid":1855790,"uid":6783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a8d09bd7ef1fa0c27f8791343222b52c621e3e0f","tid":1855790,"uid":254504,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"正 追鳩住佢噴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"無啊 噴完佢佢訓低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17f72845e4885b46d090a1e44661aeddefbc9c9","tid":1855790,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"下次屙督尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecaacc4570647f49abdfcbe7caa50e92bc1b14d","tid":1855790,"uid":6783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e17f72845e4885b46d090a1e44661aeddefbc9c9","tid":1855790,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"下次屙督尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"邊敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多人望住<br />\n同埋個陣未出黃大仙廟"},{"pid":"02e80c5bc8252a51c549d6059983bb968017bea0","tid":1855790,"uid":336046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:27:04.000Z","msg":"咁醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4206011ef5ec1c2f27c60cfc4e5eac475e2c5ad6","tid":1855790,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"飲食台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717f69c0976ca27257f4bfddbe18ebf8a6694f68","tid":1855790,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617798f2a7d742b97426b859b063473dcdffe47e","tid":1855790,"uid":295442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:39:30.000Z","msg":"在香港D阿伯食煙，通街吐痰幾十年，無犯法㗎！立條緊急法，不可以傷風囉？！"},{"pid":"16bda50fc0e1d70282b1f8a085fbd95654436dc0","tid":1855790,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30b6189f4964cb5de2ad4f3b5e321f8e5bae15e","tid":1855790,"uid":6783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4206011ef5ec1c2f27c60cfc4e5eac475e2c5ad6","tid":1855790,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"飲食台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"吐口水嘛"},{"pid":"c0ae1b6c9f5b00c70770061b03d5f7c81f866f6c","tid":1855790,"uid":269934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"多謝手足"},{"pid":"19731569adced163dab92d045e8fed04180483fd","tid":1855790,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"Mon post狗以為自己神打上身刀槍不入<br />\n區區武漢肺炎驚乜春<br />\n係咪咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19626a991f7c6d65c084279b8aa17df3f024cd66","tid":1855790,"uid":65178,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"佢哋班撚樣先係曱甴同過街老鼠喎<br />\n<br />\n我個人上會全力推廣仇恨黑警既概念<br />\n<br />\n無論黑警做乜都係有陰謀 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警講乜都係大話 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警有咩行動都係犯罪 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警想做咩洗白都唔會原諒 只有死全家呢個結局 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警係咪我自己既家屬 都會立即割席 我一齊死都無問題 唔會分析<br />\n無論係咩人支持黑警同情黑警都係我敵人 唔會分析<br />\n<br />\n我會慢慢提倡俾身邊人 教我既後代 再叫佢地宣揚出去 生生世世永不原諒港共黑警<br />\n落地獄啦你班仆街狗閪<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 831 929 101 112 113 1111 1112 1117 1118 新屋嶺 還眼 還命 被自殺 實彈 周同學 陳同學 雞姦 強姦 輪姦 因姦成孕 中大理大之戰 人踩人 濫捕<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢串事件 連杯曱甴都做唔到嘅<br />\n唔好同人講你要光復香港 直接死咗去好過 唔好浪費地球資源"},{"pid":"40dcac1b4f10f13acd4e575cb6934f6600733fc7","tid":1855790,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:26:25.000Z","msg":"口水襲警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8b355d2ce280d6897c40cfa97f4a28750546c9","tid":1855790,"uid":49853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/d7/b5/f1/d7b5f15c546de58165c9b79ad1c9244a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fd7%2Fb5%2Ff1%2Fd7b5f15c546de58165c9b79ad1c9244a.gif&h=58fadb89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直接口爆佢啦"},{"pid":"0562f94bc7bc7474f0045791657d1da0f40f3f78","tid":1855790,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8b355d2ce280d6897c40cfa97f4a28750546c9","tid":1855790,"uid":49853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/d7/b5/f1/d7b5f15c546de58165c9b79ad1c9244a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http